description:
This is a 15 minute workout called 'Full Body Stretch | Mobility Routine for Flexibility & Relaxation' from the channel growingannanas.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching and Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Ready for a Smooth Stretch Routine? I love doing Mobility Workouts before Bed, or after my workout, but you can do it whenever you want - as long as you're doing it!

Mobility is Key for many Exercises, so make sure to work on your full range of motion next to strength and hiit training!
